<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>OCR</title>
    <style>
        .image_size {
            width: 350px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .header_text,
        .body_div {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px auto;
        }


        .image_div {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .first_div {
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="body_div">
    <h1 class="header_text">OCR web app And Image Color Remove/Delete.</h1>

    <h2>Task : 1</h2>
    <h2>Takes the below image as an input and shows the text output using OCR.</h2>

    <div class="image_div">

        <div class="first_div">
            <h3>Code Image Input</h3>
            <img src="images/test1.png" class="image_size" alt="">
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>Text Image </h3>
            <img src="images/textResult.png" class="image_size" alt="">
        </div>
    </div>
    <form id="frmUploader" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/upload" method="post">
        <input type="file" name="image" multiple />

        <input type="submit" name="submit" id="btnSubmit" value="Upload" />
    </form>
    <br>
    <div style=" margin-bottom: 500px;">

        <h2>Task : 2</h2>
        <h2>select a specific colour from the image and delete it.</h2>
        <h4>For Testing Purpose</h4>

        <div class="image_div">


            <div class="first_div">
                <h3>Original Image </h3>
                <img src="images/Artwork.png" class="image_size" alt="">
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Updated Image</h3>
                <img src="images/1655732187441.000000output.jpg" class="image_size" alt="">
            </div>




        </div>

        <form id="frmUploader" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/change" method="post">
            <input type="file" name="change" multiple />


            <select name="colorHex" id="colorHex">
                <option value="#f1e502" style="background-image:url('images/1.png');">Yellow </option>
                <option value="#cbf003" style="background-image:url('images/2.png');">Greenish Yellow</option>
                <option value="#e901aa" style="background-image:url('images/3.png');">Reddish Magenta
                </option>
                <option value="#01e8c8" style="background-image:url('images/4.png');">Aqua
                </option>
                <option value="#a28886" style="background-image:url('images/5.png');">Warm Grey
                </option>
            </select>


            <input type="submit" name="submit" id="btnChangeSubmit" value="change" />


        </form>
    </div>
</body>

</html>